					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p140900">Re: I've migrated to Windows 7</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=140900#p140900"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon Feb 09, 2015 12:04 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
